  "slug": "burger-hunger",
  "title": "Burger Hunger",
  "description": "Replaces the default hunger bar with fun burger-themed icons.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">Replaces Minecraft’s default hunger bar textures with custom burger icons for a fun, food-themed UI change.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7cea5aa4fe0556f06983272d4e9e217e0b539bf9.png\" alt=\"Burger Hunger Title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">Supports AppleSkin Mod</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6c7f46cb76708a7a86efe8a31494b14f6629a471.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/cdd4b8f234ffaa59fe8b96ee22f0b620ae6d7580.png\" alt=\"Burger\" width=\"200\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/63a070f985a129b9bc282d278a725b634959c79b.png\" alt=\"Sick Burger\" width=\"200\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/76379c3b82afd540cc949635ca35d52ea8e8fd03.png\" alt=\"Supported Mods\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack fully supports the AppleSkin mod, ensuring that hunger, saturation, exhaustion, and all related HUD elements are displayed correctly with the custom textures.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">All AppleSkin overlays and indicators integrate seamlessly with the burger-style hunger bar without visual issues.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">This ensures full compatibility while preserving AppleSkin’s detailed food and saturation mechanics.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>AppleSkin</summary>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d37d25001f2297f27f257a35417dc1c83749de0f.gif\" alt=\"AppleSkin\" width=\"900\"></p>\n</details>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/black-pink-gui\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
